 Summary:	Shows the use of the IF-ELSE-THEN control structure.
 License:	CC0

 This file is part of the DeltaForth Code Samples. )

10 constant num

: main			\ Entry point
	num 2 mod	\ Remainder of division by 2
	num .		\ Display constant
	if ." is an odd number"
	else ." is an even number"
	then
;
